" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/isTrusted\"><code>isTrusted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/originalTarget\"><code>originalTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/returnValue\"><code>returnValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/srcElement\"><code>srcElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Event/target\"><code>target</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Event/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Event/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>composedPath()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>initEvent()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault\"><code>preventDefault()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/stopImmediatePropagation\"><code>stopImmediatePropagation()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Event/stopPropagation\"><code>stopPropagation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Metoda służy do zainicjalizowania zdarzenia utworzonego za pomocą <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-document\" rel=\" noopener\">interfejsu DocumentEvent</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">event.initKeyEvent(<i>type</i>,<i>bubbles</i>,<i>cancelable</i>)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">\n  <code>type</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  Typ zdarzenia.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <code>bubbles</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  Wartość logiczna wskazująca, czy zdarzenie ma bąbelkować czy nie (zob. <a href=\"pl/DOM/event.bubbles\">bubbles</a>).</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">\n  <code>cancelable</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  Wartość logiczna wskazująca, czy zdarzenie może zostać anulowane (zob. <a href=\"pl/DOM/event.cancelable\">cancelable</a>).</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">// utwórz zdarzenie kliknięcia, które bąbelkuje\n// i nie może być anulowane\nevent.initEvent(\"click\", true, false);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Zdarzenia inicjalizowane w ten sposób muszą zostać utworzone za pomocą metody <a href=\"pl/DOM/document.createEvent\">createEvent</a> interfejsu DocumentEvent. Metoda <b>initEvent</b> musi być wywołana by ustawić zdarzenie przed jego wywołaniem (za pomocą <a href=\"pl/DOM/element.dispatchEvent\">dispatchEvent</a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2001/WD-DOM-Level-3-Events-20010823/events.html#Events-Event-initEvent\" rel=\" noopener\">initEvent</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect4\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Metoda służy do zainicjalizowania zdarzenia utworzonego za pomocą interfejsu DocumentEvent","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"event.initEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"event.initEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Event.initEvent()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/event/initevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/event/initevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Event","title":"Event"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Event/initEvent","title":"event.initEvent"}],"pageTitle":"event.initEvent - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}